* {{ill|Tottori Prefecture|ja|鳥取県}} {{ill|Saiboku District|ja|西伯郡}} {{ill|Nanbu Town|ja|南部町 (鳥取県)|lt=Nanbu Town|lt_ja=南部町}} Yamato 3

=== Transportation Access ===
* From {{ill|JR West|ja|西日本旅客鉄道|lt=JR}} on the {{ill|Sanin Main Line|ja|山陰本線}} at {{ill|Yonago Station|ja|米子駅}}, take the {{ill|Hinomarudōsha|ja|日ノ丸自動車}} bus on the Hōshōji Line to “Yamato Bus Stop” (approximately 18 minutes). Then walk for about 11 minutes.

