=== Transportation Access ===
* From {{ill|JR West|ja|西日本旅客鉄道|lt=JR|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Sanin Main Line|ja|山陰本線|12=draft}} at {{ill|Yonago Station|ja|米子駅|12=draft}}, take the {{ill|Hinomarudōsha|ja|日ノ丸自動車|12=draft}} bus on the Hōshōji Line to “Yamato Bus Stop” (approximately 18 minutes). Then walk for about 11 minutes.

