* Toyoiwato-no-mikoto (at {{ill|Hokuhō Shrine|ja|北方神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: May Taishō 5; at {{ill|Aga Shrine|ja|阿賀神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: April 30, Taishō 6)
* {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主|lt=Ōkuninushi|lt_ja=大己貴命|12=draft|12=draft}} (at {{ill|Kobara Shrine|ja|小原神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: merged May Taishō 5)
* {{ill|Sukunabikona|ja|スクナビコナ|lt=Sukunabikona|lt_ja=少彦名命|12=draft|12=draft}} (at {{ill|Kobara Shrine|ja|小原神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: merged May Taishō 5)
* {{ill|Ukano Mitama|ja|ウカノミタマ|lt=Ukano Mitama|lt_ja=倉稲魂命|12=draft|12=draft}} (at {{ill|Tanabe Shrine|ja|田邊神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: merged April 30, Taishō 6)
* {{ill|Susanoo|ja|スサノオ|lt=Susanoo|lt_ja=素戔嗚命|12=draft|12=draft}} (at {{ill|Aga Shrine|ja|阿賀神社|12=draft|12=draft}}: merged April 30, Taishō 6)

